metadata.othernotes:
Sanako Isogai (Sanae Furukawa) is Nagisa's Furukawa's mother

If in a game with Nagisa, Sanae is there to watch over her daughter and make sure she is safe. The knowledge of the mother-daughter relationship will always be one way: Nagisa will never learn that her mother is playing. Because Sanako is not sexually interested in her own daughter, there is no chance of incest.

If Nagisa is not present, Sanae is here to flirt away some of the stress of married life. But she has no intention of having intercourse. Despite probably being in her late thirties, Sanae has a youthful appearance that can easily pass for someone of Nagisa's age.
